  "descriptions": {
    "en": {
      "language": "en",
      "value": "military commander from the Sengoku period to the Azuchi-Momoyama period. A wealthy native of Todo Village, Inukami District, Omi. 8th generation of Todo clan. Sadajo Mitsui - Sadaji Mitsui - Noritsuna Mitsui - Torataka Torataka Todo"
    },
    "ja": {
      "language": "ja",
      "value": "戦国時代から安土桃山時代の武将。近江犬上郡藤堂村の土豪。藤堂氏8代。三井定条-三井定仍-三井乗綱（近江鯰江城主）-藤堂虎高（次男）。仕武田信虎"
    },
    "nl": {
      "language": "nl",
      "value": "commandant"
    }
